{"tid":1753183,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你知道我們每鬆懈多1440分鐘，香港就會","createTime":"2019-11-25T01:44:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T08:02:07.000Z","uid":41423,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b339691ed6c41acdabed811db484209da7c2968e","tid":1753183,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T01:44:52.000Z","msg":"港共政府就會有多一日諗唔同藉口dq民選議員，計劃推更多惡法，放更多舊中國人來香港做新香港人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n親共派就會多一日開始準備下屆立會選舉配票/種票/掌心雷。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n警甴就多一日補給裝備武器和休息。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中共網軍就多一日製造風向，輿論。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n傷亡義士就可能會被忘記多一日。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以 五大訴求 缺一不可  才是我們的真正目標。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"794a1623b5283abc801134b0e619ef045ea3707d","tid":1753183,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T02:05:42.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60e5d3c6037925b6ef79c928b119715294ebf68e","tid":1753183,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T02:57:47.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f543ac0c7e7727edb6a8104ba6cbe7600f77872c","tid":1753183,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:07:33.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a0556a0aaba7a699bba02a4c1f9b68d581b16367","tid":1753183,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:08:00.000Z","msg":"民建聯又多左一日做好地區工作收買人心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ea4e605c45518e260939a4ef65027ead504529e","tid":1753183,"uid":236878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:09:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"43b06301de